channel.title: Wizard Of Oz Suicidal Munchkin Hanging From A Tree
channel.description:
[youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SU32MewCung&feature=related[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P8YVeMwhDNI&feature=related[/youtube]
You think it's real? I'm kinda stuck in the middle... Reasons it could be: 1. It looks too good to be edited in 2. People say it's a bird. That's not a fucking bird... >.<
Reasons it couldn't be: 1. Their skipping right in front of the patch where he's hanging. Don't you think they'd see him and do something? 2. That's pretty noticeable. I even saw in the first part (100% zoom and speed), Wouldn't they see it too?
Either way, it's still really kinda creepy and odd... What do you think? Is it real? And why or why not?
